Title: Mister Spex Facematching Glasses Ultralight Classics Luton
Description: Kaufe Ultralight Classics Luton 1134 003 Brille bei Mister Spex. Du kannst einfach und bequem von zu Hause aus bestellen.
Review: They have a face-scanning app which you download. This makes Mister Spex glasses THE MOST COMFY glasses I ever posessed. Stylish frames, high-end glasses and all of that of course included. Not sure if available in the US, but definitely in the UK and Germany.

Title: Ultra Stretch Active Jogger Pants | UNIQLO
Description: Incredible stretch and a stay-fresh feel. Comfortable and highly functional. Recycled Polyester
Review:
UNIQLO is my staple-clothing brand. They just tick so many boxes: price, design and versatility. No bullshit good clothing. 

I have 4 of their long pants. You can wear them at home, on casual nights, on casual-smart nights, for sports – 100% fulfilling my preference for versatile functional apparel. They're of course also very comfy and suitable for warm or cold climates alike.

Title: AIRism Cotton UV Protection Crew Neck Long-Sleeve T-Shirt | UNIQLO
Description: Smooth 'AIRism' fabric with the look of cotton. A versatile layering piece.
Review:
Once again: UNIQLO is my staple-clothing brand. They just tick so many boxes: price, design and versatility. No bullshit good clothing. For me, UNIQLO replaced H&M, C&A, Primark, Zara etc.

The AIRism long-sleeve shirts have a timeless, simple design and they make your muscles pop a bit :) Can be used for both warmer or colder climates. Feel good on the skin and quality is decent.

Title: DRY-EX Polo Shirt | UNIQLO
Description: Quick-drying 'DRY-EX' with 3 types of mesh for lasting freshness.
Review: And another UNIQLO, breathable, versatile clothing item. This polo shirt can be used for sports or somewhat fancy outings alike. Works in cold or warm weather. Love this japanese shit.

Title: Vuori Sunday Performance Jogger
Description: Vuori's Sunday Performance Joggers provide a fresh take on athleisure and serve as the perfect staple pants in your wardrobe. Shop our men's black joggers.
Review: Like with the UNIQLO long pants, these can be worn for outings and sports alike. However, the quality is a little higher (reflected in the price). Recommended by Tim Ferriss, so I dig it.

Title: Allbirds Men's Tree Dasher 2
Description: The Tree Dasher 2 is the next evolution of our best-selling running shoe, designed to support your everyday runs, walks, and light workouts. Made with lightweight and breathable eucalyptus fiber, this shoe has lighter, more responsive foam, extra grip, padded heel collar to reduce slipping, and an improved fit to keep you running and nature winning.
Review:
Allbirds are the truly sustainable sneaker brand out there; who also happen to make stylish-af shoes. Look cool, but also very performant for sports of any kind. I use them in any weather and are currently the only non-flip-flop or tropical shoes I carry with me in my perpetual travel state.
The company aims to be carbon-zero by 2030, and they're already half-way there in 2023. Shoes are entirely made out of sustainable material. Good stuff folks. Check out their programs here: https://www.allbirds.com/pages/sustainable-practices#priorities

Title: Ocean Elastic Amphibian Shorts | Quiksilver
Description: Chilling in the morning, surfing in the afternoon. And you didn't have to change your trunks. The Ocean Elastic Waist Amphibian Short for men was made for extreme versatility. So whether the day as you ruling in the water or on dry land, you're always good to go. Styled to look like your favourite walk shorts, their high-tech surf fabric is enhanced with 4-way stretch for massive mobility. And you can rely on our DryFlight Water Repellent Hydrophobic treatment to block the water from seeping in. So you're dry and on your way in no time.
Review: Since I'm mostly around the tropics, I need a stack of high-quality shorts. And since I'm this sucker for functional multi-use clothing, I'm very much a fan of Quicksilver amphibian shorts: they can be used for swimming, sports or just going out. Very comfy and unlike most shorts, the cut suits my waist and thigh profiles. Tried other boardshort brands like Billabong, buy they're simply not as comfy, well-cut or of decent enough quality. Really like these.

Title: Taxer Cargo Amphibian Boardshorts | Quiksilver
Description: Surf at 2pm, BBQ at 5pm. And the Taxer Cargo Amphibian Boardshort has you dialed in for both. Made to be worn in and out of the water with a modern camo print, loads of flex, and a quick-dry treatment for those times when you need to hustle.
Review:
Another set of Quicksilver amphibian shorts. Same review as the other one. And I also own 3 of them in different colors.

Since I'm mostly around the tropics, I need a stack of high-quality shorts. And since I'm this sucker for functional multi-use clothing, I'm very much a fan of Quicksilver amphibian shorts: they can be used for swimming, sports or just going out. Very comfy and unlike most shorts, the cut suits my waist and thigh profiles. Tried other boardshort brands like Billabong, buy they're simply not as comfy, well-cut or of decent enough quality. Really like these.

Title: Men's UNEEK Monochrome | KEEN Footwear
Description: Solid-colored cords add distinctive style, while the one-of-a-kind cord construction molds to and flexes with your foot for a custom feel. A soft footbed kicks up the comfort factor.
Review: Usually sandals that look good also don't allow you to do much with them. With KEEN – gladiator-reminiscent sandals for which I received several compliments from strangers already for their funkiness – I played padel, went hiking and river tracing. Lasted me around 3 years of almost every-day usage, since they were also my daily shoes.

Title: Chamomile & Spearmint Tea
Description: Our chamomile and spearmint tea blend combines the calm and comfort of chamomile with the crisp, minty flavor of spearmint to create an herbal tea that is as soothing as it is refreshing.
Review: My sleep ritual is not complete without a cup of chamomile tea at night, which has soothing effects. I don't care too much about which brand since I travel so much and most brands are not available in all countries, but if I'd go for a brand I'd go for the no-nonsene Public Goods chamomile tea.

Title: New to Matcha' Full Kit with Organic Matcha
Description: Matcha Tea Kit - Full Set with Ceremonial Organic Matcha. This matcha starter set is designed with matcha newcomers in mind, but could totally work for anyone! Containing one of our highest grades of organic ceremonial matcha, all you have to do is choose your favorite color and mixing style! Leaning towards the electr
Review:
MOST MATCHAS YOU DRINK SUCK. If the powder is not a radiant viper green and already smells upon opening a can, you've been sold the watered down commercialised version in the west. Or rather, outside of Japan. If matcha is not prepared or stored correctly, it oxidizes and loses it's bright green color and natural flavor, getting too bitter instead.
Why should you drink matcha: matcha has the highest concentration of anti-oxidants and L-theanine of all green teas. 

Dr. Andrew Weil, one of the major forces in the scientific research of psychedelics, wanted to bring more high-quality matcha to the West, which is why he set up matcha.com.

More about Dr. Andrew Weil on the Tim Ferriss podcast about matcha.com https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4TEC6ZgbV_Y

Title: Tim Tam Cookies Arnotts
Description: Created in 1964, Arnott’s Tim Tam is Australia’s most loved & most iconic chocolate biscuit. Indulge in irresistible layers of Tim Tam with a mouth-watering combination of smooth chocolate coating, crunchy biscuit and a luscious velvety centre. What more could you wish for
Review:
Germans are known for being the largest per capita consumer of chocolates and chocolate snacks. WIth that, also comes the best variety of mass chocolate snacks in the world (the US may have the largest variety in general, but they have a huge proportion of truly shitty low-quality snacks, so I put Germany ahead). So it's safe to say as a child I was exposed to quite a lot of chocolate, even though with age my immediate desire and happiness for chocolate faded away. Little did I know that the best chocolate snack was actually on the other side of the world.

Upon discovering Tim Tams, just recently, I regained that childish appreciation for chocolate.  With remarkable; texture; appearance; and taste, Tim Tams are an Australian biscuit (American cookie) that you will never forget.

Texture and Appearance:
Tim Tam’s very closely resemble a Twix candy bar. Being about half the length and two to three times the width of a Twix, it has a smooth, milky exterior. The interior of the cookie has a cream, filled center that is sandwiched between two crunchy biscuits. Tim Tam’s have 10-20 cookies in each package, depending on whether you buy the regular or value pack boxes. Finally, in Australia each package is sold for no more than $2.50; but if bought online from the U.S. they can be as much as $7.00 a box.

Taste:
Tim Tams are offered in a variety of flavors ranging from chocolate, to salted caramel, to red velvet. One of the most popular flavors on the market would be the double coat flavor. Offering twice the amount of chocolate on its exterior as the regular chocolate Tim Tams, it leaves an impression on your taste buds that will leave you begging for more. These cookies are known for causing binge eating; meaning the cookies are so tasty, that people often finish the whole package in one sitting.

Availability:
The only downside to Tim Tams is they're hard to find outside of Australia. The off-brand American Tim Tams can be found at your local Target, but they just don't have quite the same effect as the Australian version. Otherwise, your only other options are to buy it online or find a “world food store” that might possibly have them in stock; which can cause them to be expensive due to shipping and rarity costs.

I truly think Tim Tams are the best cookies you can buy. Even though they can be hard to find, I would recommend them to everyone. With a taste and texture that puts it above all other cookies, it’s no surprise they have taken Australia by storm.

Title: Sanpellegrino Italian Sparkling Drink Limonata
Description: Enjoy every sparkling moment with Sanpellegrino Limonata Sparkling Drinks. Sanpellegrino Limonata sparkling beverage is a lemon flavored sparkling beverage made with Italian lemons containing real lemon juice (16% juice from concentrate), sugar and other natural flavors to add a refreshing alternative to traditional seltzer water, flavored sparkling water or carbonated soft drinks. With deliciously sweet tartness, this flavored sparkling beverage is made with no artificial sweeteners. Smooth on the palate, Sanpellegrino Limonata is a delicately balanced drink with fresh and tart notes, with the perfect sweet touch to end. Enjoy Sanpellegrino Limonata as a refreshing sparkling drink, a tasty mid-afternoon treat or while you unwind at the end of the day. Serve this flavored sparkling beverage chilled, and garnish with fresh berries or mint for an expert finish. Whatever the occasion, take the time for taste with a Sanpellegrino Italian sparkling drinks.
Review:
I have only a few truly bad habits in terms of nutrition. One of them would be that I could be heating low-carb, highly-nutrutious meals with lots of fish and veggies throughout the day, but then chug it all down with 2-3 cans of fucking good lemonade.

Forget coke, fanta and all that bullshit. San Pellegrino has the best soda out there, and it is a simple lemonade made of Italian lemons. I saw some other brands that also embrace this concept, but San Pellegrino are the most available around the world. It's just so good. It's the perfect unhealthy drink which doesn't taste like you're just drinking artificially created chemical compounds (like Dr. Pepper or shit like that).

Title: Exquisa Käsekuchen-Snack Natur (70g)
Description: The first cheesecake on the cooling shelf. Baked with cream cheese - making it particularly juicy and tasty.
Review: I vividly remember eating loads of these as a 3-year old. Simple cheese cakes wrapped like twix. But it's cheese cake. And it's delicisious, to this day. Perfect for a lunch box for travel.

Title: Ferrero Hanuta Minis
Description: Ferrero Hanuta Minis in Bag 6.2 oz
Review: After Tim Tam, Hanuta has to be the best mass-produced chocolate snack out there. Ferrerro is just a master at this and superior to most American confectionary brands.

Title: Deliciously Creamy Barista Blend Oat Milk | Oatside
Description: Join the plant milk revolution with our Barista Blend. Creamy mouthfeel, perfectly balanced & frothy perfection. No more 'kinda weird' taste! Buy now.
Review: I still prefer regular whole milk, but every once in a while I like to mix things up or want a less heavy supplement for the coffee. Oatside is the first oatmilk I tried where I wasn't immediately put off.

Title: BanyuaTis Bali Coffee Kopi Bali
Description: Bali Kopi Bubuk
Review: My morning coffee is usually bali coffee – similar to Turkish coffee.

Title: Instant Vortex Plus 6-Quart Air Fryer Oven
Description: This Instant™ Vortex® Plus has a ton of useful features, but top of the list has to be the ClearCook window. The see-through window works with a perfectly placed light inside so you can check on cooking progress without opening the basket. The EvenCrisp™ air flow technology delivers crispy, tender results every time with 95% less oil. 6 cooking programs give you one-touch access to easy recipes, but let you customize for yourself. And because the cooking basket and cooking trays are non-stick and dishwasher safe, clean-up is a snap.
Review: You'll be less lazy to cook with an airfryer, and you'll also be more healthy using less oil. I believe air fryers are a must for modern cooking. And for value for money, the Instant Vortex is wins.

Title: Mario Kart 8 Deluxe
Description: Hit the road with the definitive version of Mario Kart 8 and play anytime, any-where! Race your friends or battle them in a revised battle mode on new and returning battle courses. Play locally in up to 4-player multiplayer in 1080p while playing in TV Mode. Every track from the Wii U version, including DLC, makes a glorious return. Plus, the Inklings appear as all-new guest characters, along with returning favorites, such as King Boo, Dry Bones, and Bowser Jr.!
Review: A dependable classic. Great as a party game with flatmates, or alone rising up the ranks so you end up playing only with Japanese and Koreans.

Title: The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild
Description:
Forget everything you know about The Legend of Zelda games. Step into a world of discovery, exploration and adventure in The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild, a boundary-breaking game in the acclaimed series.

• Step into a world of discovery, exploration and adventure in The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild
• Explore a world of unprecedented size and discover more than 100 puzzle-filled shrines, plus a wide variety of weapons, outfits and gear
• Climb up towers and mountain peaks in search of destinations, then set your own path to get there and plunge into the wilderness; along the way, you'll battle towering enemies, hunt wild beasts and gather ingredients for the food and elixirs you'll need to sustain you on your journey
• Shrines dot the landscape, waiting to be discovered in any order you want; search for them in various ways and solve a variety of puzzles inside; work your way through the traps and devices inside to earn special items and other rewards that will help you on your adventure
• Enjoy the adventure on the TV or escape to Hyrule on-the-go in handheld mode.Compatible with Nintendo Switch only
Review: Critically one of the most perfect games every developed, in one if the most beloved game franchises of history.

Title: The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom
Description:
An epic adventure across the land and skies of Hyrule awaits in The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom for Nintendo Switch. The adventure is yours to create in a world fueled by your imagination. In this sequel to The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild, you’ll decide your own path through the sprawling landscapes of Hyrule and the mysterious islands floating in the vast skies above. Can you harness the power of Link’s new abilities to fight back against the malevolent forces that threaten the kingdom?

• Ultrahand: Using the new Ultrahand ability, Link can pick up, move, and rotate almost any object, and can even attach objects together to create bridges, vehicles, and more!
• Fuse: Magically fuse almost any object to Link’s current weapon, shield, or arrow to increase durability, damage, or even add a new effect. Experiment with lots of different combinations to come up with surprising—and sometimes hilarious—results!
• Ascend: Add a new dimension to your exploration with Ascend, which gives Link the ability to pass through solid objects above him. Rise up through ceilings, hillsides, and even certain enemies to create seemingly impossible shortcuts.
• Recall: Use Recall to make objects in motion move backward through time, letting Link ride fallen boulders skyward, recover thrown weapons, or send projectiles back where they came from.
Review: Apparently even better than the precursor The Breath of the Wild.

Title: Sid Meier's Civilization VI
Description:
Those who purchase Civilization VI for PlayStation 4 will also receive as a bonus the following pieces of additional content: Nubia Civilization & Scenario Pack and Khmer Indonesia Civilization & Scenario Pack. Originally created by legendary game designer Sid Meier, Civilization is a turn-based strategy game in which you attempt to build an empire to stand the test of time. Explore a new land, research technology, conquer your enemies, and go head-to-head with history’s most renowned leaders as you attempt to build the greatest civilization the world has ever known.

• Expansive Empires: see the marvels of your empire spread across the map. Settle in Uncharted lands, improve your surroundings, build new districts, and see your cities and Your civilization prosper
• Active research: unlock boosts that speed your civilization's progress through history. To advance more quickly, use your units to actively explore, develop your environment, and discover new cultures.
• Dynamic diplomacy: interactions with other civilizations change over the course of the game, from primitive first interactions where conflict is a fact of life, to late game alliances and negotiations.
Review: An absolute joy if you're a culture and history fan, and a natural-born strategist with world-domination fantasies. My approach is to go all-out on commerce and then get to the point where I can just nuke blast all nations of the world into submission of the Vincent's Grand Empire MUAHAHAHHAAH

Title: Age of Mythology
Description:
From the makers of Age of Empires comes a strategy game where the line between history and mythology has been blurred. In Age of Mythology heroes do battle with monsters of legend, and the gods intervene in the affairs of mortal men. Age of Mythology players wage war as leaders of a Greek, Norse, or Egyptian civilization with a customized pantheon. Players use human armies and diplomacy, progress through development ages, enhance military and economic performance with improvements, and manage economics through resource gathering and trade. Mythology enters the mix when players call upon the gods to act on their behalf or reinforce their armies with more than 20 mythological creatures such as jackal-headed Egyptian warriors or mighty minotaurs. Age of Mythology's revolutionary 3-D engine provides the game with gorgeous environments featuring lifelike rolling terrain, beautiful waves and water, realistic sunlight, and lush forests. The units roaming these environments are incredibly detailed, move naturally over the terrain, and come to life through hundreds of fluid animations. Amazing special effects change the look of this beautiful world when the gods get involved: all grows dark as an eclipse takes effect, funnel clouds twist and grow as a tornado sends buildings spinning toward the heavens, and meteors streak in from the heavens to send people and armies flying. An entertaining tutorial, an intuitive interface, and logical game rules allow anyone to quickly and easily learn to play. Once started, there is a lot to explore: an epic 36 scenario single player campaign, easy-to-use multiplayer gaming online, single player games against the challenging Age of Mythology AI opponents, more than 15 different random map types that help make the game infinitely replayable, nine highly differentiated civilizations, multiple difficulty levels to allow players of any skill level to have an enjoyable game, and a fully functional scenario editor. Age of Mythology offers something for everyone: a fun game for any playing style or skill level. In Age of Mythology heroes do battle with monsters of legend, and the gods intervene in the affairs of mortal men. Age of Mythology offers something for everyone: a fun game for any playing style or skill level.

• The game is only played on the computer and is not available for online play.
• In this exciting real-time strategy game, youplay as either the ancient Greeks, Norse or Egyptians. All three are vying for control of the world, and you must help your chosen side to succeed!
• To control more territory, you'll have to arrange armies, handle diplomacy and manage trade
• Technological improvements combine with supernatural power as you develop your sciences and call upon the ancient gods
• Rain down lightning on an opposing army, demolish enemy camps with earthquakes, and sink a navy with a tidal wave -- you'll see it all happen in real-time with incredibly detailed special effects
• You can also reinforce your armies with over 20 legendary monsters
Review: Age of Empires had a little spin-off in the early 2000s, and for me it's the best strategy game ever made. As a big fan of history and mythology, this 100% struck a chord with me and made me wonder when we'll have those mythology movies coming out – which eventually happened.

Title: Warcraft III
Description: This epic pack includes 2002 Game of the Year, Warcraft III: The Reign of Chaos, Warcraft III Expansion: The Frozen Throne and official strategy guides for both games. The Warcraft III Battle Chest is the ultimate collection of the best-selling Blizzard strategy games. This set includes 2002 Game of the Year Warcraft III: The Reign of Chaos, as well as the recently released and critically acclaimed follow-up - Warcraft III Expansion: The Frozen Throne. In addition to all these hours of epic adventure in the world of Azeroth, and limitless online fun on the Battle.net gaming site, the Battle Chest also contains strategy guides from Brady Games for both titles to help players dominate the battlefield. This collection is valued at over $75.00 sold separately, and is perfect for entering the epic war between the races of Azeroth and the demonic Burning Legion.
Review: This has to be another favorite strategy game. So well conceptualised, so pleasing to conquer. And I can vainly say I played the rugged precursor to all the Dota and League of Legends games, which  were the Hero Wars online battle modes (hosted by players themselves), before online gaming was a mainstream movement.

Title: Ultimate Chicken Horse
Description: Ever wish you were a wall-jumping, arrow-dodging, trap-setting Horse, besting your animal Pals in a race through a peril-laden obstacles course that you all built together? Wish granted! Ultimate Chicken Horse is a party platformer where you and your friends build the level as you play, placing deadly traps before trying to reach the end of the level. If you can make it but your friends can't, you score points! Play online or locally with your animal buddies and experiment with a wide variety of platforms to find new ways to mess with your friends. Customizable your rule sets and game modes and even create, save, and share custom levels. Challenge your friends to beat your levels and monitor with global leaderboards. Play as a Chicken, Horse, sheep, and other wonderful animals presented in a fun cartoony art style.
Review: One of the best party games out there, full-stop. Funny, easy to get into, and it will cause a lot of laughter and competitive trash talk.

Title: Cards Against Humanity: Nasty Bundle
Description:
The Nasty Bundle is an abominable collection of the spiciest expansion packs we've ever written. It contains cards previously released in the Period Pack, Weed Pack, Ass Pack, Saves America Pack, and Picture Card Packs, plus a handful of brand-new cards we wrote just for you sickos. Shuffle these into your regular set of Cards Against Humanity and make everyone uncomfortable at game night.

• The Nasty Bundle is a collection of six themed packs that's too spicy for most stores. Shuffle these into your deck and make everyone uncomfortable the next time you play!
• Includes the Period Pack, Weed Pack, Ass Pack, Saves America Pack, Picture Card Pack 1, and Picture Card Pack 2.
• This is an expansion. Requires the Cards Against Humanity main game.
• Ages 17+
• Also includes ten all-new extra-nasty cards we wrote just for you.
Review: No need to explain this gem of a party game, where dark humor (the best humor) get's free reign from political correctness or appropriatness.

Title: Poetry for Neanderthals by Exploding Kittens LLC
Description:
Poetry for Neanderthals is a family-friendly party game similar to Taboo where players earn points by getting their teammates to guess words and phrases. The catch is that the "Neanderthal Poets" are only allowed to use single syllable words. If they use any words with more than one syllable, the other team gets to bop them with a 2-foot inflatable club. The team with the most points wins!

• MAKE PARTY GREAT: We have fun game. Help team guess word on card. Catch is, use only one sound. No big words or boom stick hit you! Poetry for Neanderthals is the guessing game that needs you to channel your inner caveman. Speak in single syllables and win points with every correct guess. If you start talking fancy, someone from the opposing team gets to bop you with an inflatable club. Looking for a party game for kids and adults that will have the crowd roaring with laughter? You’ve found it!
• COMPLETE GAME SET: You’ll have everything you need. Just call your crew, tell them to leave their grammar at the door, and let the games begin. You’ll receive 200 double-sided cards, 2 game boards, and a 2-foot inflatable No! Stick, and 1 sand timer. And we know you’ll get a bit too enthusiastic with the inflated club- it’s hard not to. That’s why we’ve thrown in a repair patch with each of the card games for families. In case anything happens, just patch it up, and keep on guessing.
• WHOLE FAMILY FUN: Kids will love it. Teens won’t get enough of it. Adults will be scrambling to get their own copy. Meet your new game night staple. Poetry for Neanderthals is great for grownups & kids ages 7+ and accommodates 2-6 players. The more of your primitive family and friends you bring in on the fun, the more knee-slapping hilarity will ensue. Break it out after dinner, on lazy weekends, during picnics, or at work when your boss has gone for that conference.
• ELEVATE THE EXCITEMENT: It make fun big plus big. Laugh loud plus loud. Pal will greet hand. Tell you praise. Say top day of life …. We’re talking about the Poetry for Neanderthals expansion pack! (And we know we’d get bopped a few times there. We live dangerously) The More Cards Box 1 adds 2,000 new words and phrases. Think you can do better than our Neanderthal brains? We’ve also included 20 blank cards that give you the power to personalize the game.
• WELCOME TO THE FAMILY: Poetry for Neanderthals is created by the same guys that gave you Exploding Kittens - an idea first launched on Kickstarter. We aimed to raise $10K. We ended up with $8.7M in 30 days from 219,000 backers. Close to a decade later, Exploding Kittens is still the #1 most-backed project in Kickstarter history. We’ve since launched the likes of Throw Throw Burrito, Really Loud Librarians, and more game-night-boosting goodness. Collect them all and brace yourself for epic fun!
Review: From the makers of Exploding Kittens, this new board game will is another party favorite.

Title: Starfield: Standard Edition
Description:
• Pre-order now and receive “Old Mars Skin Pack” in-game bonus skins
• Start your journey by customizing your appearance and deciding your Background and Traits
• Venture through the stars and explore more than 1000 planets
• Pilot and command the ship of your dreams.
Review: As someone who is a very light and princess-like sleeper, who doesn't do well with warmth and can barely sleep with someone else even in the same room, this is a relationship-saver.

List: Presents You Can Bribe Me With
Title: X-Box Series  X + Starfield Bundle
Description:
• XBOX SERIES X: The fastest, most powerful Xbox ever. Explore rich new worlds with 12 teraflops of raw graphic processing power, DirectX ray tracing, a custom SSD, and 4K gaming.*FASTER LOAD TIMES: Make the most of every gaming minute with Quick Resume, lightning-fast load times, and gameplay of up to 120 FPS – all powered by Xbox Velocity Architecture.
• LOOKS AND PLAYS BEST: Enjoy thousands of games from four generations of Xbox, with hundreds of optimized titles that look and play better than ever.
• PRE-ORDER BONUS: Receive "Old Mars Skin Pack" in-game bonus featuring Deep Mining Helmet & Pack and Laser Cutter.
• EXPLORE OUTER SPACE: Venture through the stars and explore more than 1000 planets. Navigate bustling cities, explore dangerous bases, and traverse wild landscapes.
• TELL YOUR STORY: Start your journey by customizing your appearance and deciding your Background and Traits. Will you be an experienced explorer, a charming diplomat, a stealthy cyber runner, or something else entirely? The choice is yours.
Review: I just want to play Starfield. And I'm willing to get an X-Box for that.

List: Presents You Can Bribe Me With
Title: Apple Vision Pro
Description: Apple Vision Pro seamlessly blends digital content with your physical space. So you can do the things you love in ways never before possible.
Review: This is basically an ultimate vanity purchase. But as a tech-head it's a must vanity-purchase. It's so fucking cool.

List: Presents You Can Bribe Me With
Title: Pro Display XDR
Description: Pro Display XDR. A new 32-inch Retina 6K display with extreme brightness, contrast, color accuracy, and HDR that transforms the way you work.
Review: Another completely unecessary, overly expensive item. Why not just a curved 4k screen? I don't know.

List: Presents You Can Bribe Me With
Title: Cube Sleep System: Consistent Bed Climate with Chilipad
Description: Fall asleep faster with the Cube sleep system, our heating & cooling mattress pad. A thermostat for your bed, with temperature ranging from 55-115°F. Shop now.
Review: As someone who is a very light and princess-like sleeper, who doesn't do well with warmth and can barely sleep with someone else even in the same room, this is a relationship-saver.

List: Presents You Can Bribe Me With
Title: Starfield: Standard Edition
Description:
Starfield is the first new universe in over 25 years from Bethesda Game Studios, the award-winning creators of The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim and Fallout 4. In this next generation role-playing game set amongst the stars, create any character you want and explore with unparalleled freedom as you embark on an epic journey to answer humanity’s greatest mystery. In the year 2330, humanity has ventured beyond our solar system, settling new planets, and living as a spacefaring people. You will join Constellation – the last group of space explorers seeking rare artifacts throughout the galaxy – and navigate the vast expanse of space in Bethesda Game Studios’ biggest and most ambitious game.

• Pre-order now and receive “Old Mars Skin Pack” in-game bonus skins
• Start your journey by customizing your appearance and deciding your Background and Traits
• Venture through the stars and explore more than 1000 planets
• Pilot and command the ship of your dreams.
Review: Because it's going to be the best game of the decade. Full stop. Skyrim was the best game of the last decade, and this will be the best game of this decade.

Title: Manta Sleep Mask
Description: Our founders started Manta Sleep after using light leaking, sweaty, cheaply-made sleep masks for over 15 years. Until one morning, they hit their breaking point. 11 design iterations, 25 manufacturing partners and 30 fabric evaluations later, the first Manta Sleep Mask was born. We think most sleep companies focus on the wrong things. To us, sleep itself isn’t that important — it’s what you do with the energy great sleep gives you. We work to improve and optimize sleep so you have the energy to create your best life. We believe that better sleep enables your best life — and that an afternoon nap can transform your day. We get to contribute to better lives every single day by improving the sleep of our customers: 400,000+ and counting. And we love that. Visit the Store
Review: Most sleep masks are uncomfortable and simply suck. This mask feels like a gentle cloud caressing your face. No more shitty sleep in bedrooms without blinders and strong external lights.

Title: Cooling Weighted Blanket | Gravity Blankets
Description: Hot sleeper? Don't sweat it - Order our new and improved cooling weighted blanket to experience your most comfortable night of sleep yet. You won't regret it.
Review: Any gravity blanket is fine, but this is probably the best brand. But yeah, I cannot sleep with regular blankets anymore. Gravity blankets feel like you're permanently hugged, and if it's a good brand they also have some cooling effect.

Title: Dream Pillow Set - Helix Sleep
Description: Get ready for sleep bliss. Our Dream Pillows have a down alternative design and include a 100% cotton plain weave cover. The pillows have a polyester filling including 50% conjugated polyester fiber and 50% polyester microfiber. The Dream Pillows are designed with a plush, supportive feel.
Review: In accordance with my princely sleep requirements, a superior ergonomic pilliw into which my precious head can sink is a must. Obviously cooling as well.

Title: Cube Sleep System: Consistent Bed Climate with Chilipad
Description: Fall asleep faster with the Cube sleep system, our heating & cooling mattress pad. A thermostat for your bed, with temperature ranging from 55-115°F. Shop now.
Review: As someone who is a very light and princess-like sleeper, who doesn't do well with warmth and can barely sleep with someone else even in the same room, this is a relationship-saver.

Title: Google Pixel 7-5G Android Phone
Description:
Meet Google Pixel 7. Powered by Google Tensor G2, it’s fast and secure, with amazing battery life and the advanced Pixel Camera for beautifully authentic, accurate photos with Real Tone and stunning video with Cinematic Blur. Plus, it’s Pixel’s most refined design, made with recycled materials.

• Unlocked Android 5G phone gives you the flexibility to change carriers and choose your own data plan[2]; works with Google Fi, Verizon, T-Mobile, AT&T, and other major carriers
• Pixel’s Adaptive Battery can last over 24 hours; when Extreme Battery Saver is turned on, it can last up to 72 hours[3]
• The 6.3-inch Pixel 7 display is super sharp, with rich, vivid colors; it’s fast and responsive for smoother gaming, scrolling, and moving between apps[4]
• Google Pixel 7 has wide and ultrawide lenses with up to 8x Super Res Zoom[5]; and Cinematic Blur brings more drama to your videos
• With Google Tensor G2 and the Titan M2 security chip, your Pixel is built with multiple layers of security to help keep your personal info safe
• VPN by Google One (coming soon) is built into your Pixel 7 to help protect your online activity, no matter what app or web browser you use[6]
Review: I just didn't get the hang of iPhones yet. I'm a full-on Androidian, and Google arguably has the best Android phone out there. Since I use everything Google (Photos, Cloud, Docs etc.) this syncs quite nicely.

Title: Bose QuietComfort 45
Description:
The first noise cancelling headphones are back, with world-class quiet, lightweight materials, and proprietary technology for deep, clear sound and adjustable EQ so you can tune your music to your liking. Bose QuietComfort 45 headphones aren’t just an icon reborn – they’re the perfect balance of quiet, comfort, and sound. Plus, everything that made the first around ear headphones an icon is still here. Just refined. Like an updated design with smooth cushions and a clean look. Plush synthetic leather, impact-resistant glass-filled nylon, and cast-metal hinges were all selected for their comfort as well as their durability. Add in minimal clamping force, and you’ll almost forget you’re wearing Bluetooth wireless noise cancelling headphones. Enhanced Acoustic Noise Cancelling™ technology produces the true quiet needed to hear every detail of your music in high fidelity. Or, choose the new Aware Mode to hear your music and your environment together. TriPort acoustic architecture and Bose's innovative Volume-optimized Active EQ add depth and clarity while maintaining balance at any volume. And lightweight materials such as synthetic leather and glass-filled nylon were meticulously selected for comfort and durability. The headphones offer 24 hours of play time*, charge via USB-C®, and feature six microphones for clearer calls. Bluetooth® 5.1 maintains a strong connection, and the Bose Music app guides you through setup, lets you personalize settings, and keeps your headphones’ software up to date.

• NOISE CANCELLING WIRELESS HEADPHONES: The perfect balance of quiet, comfort, and sound. Bose uses tiny mics to measure, compare, and react to outside noise, cancelling it with opposite signals. Bluetooth range-up to 9 m (30 feet).
• HIGH-FIDELITY AUDIO: The TriPort acoustic architecture offers depth and fullness. Volume-optimized Active EQ maintains balanced performance at any volume, so bass stays consistent when turned down and the music remains clear when turned up.
• QUIET AND AWARE MODES: Choose Quiet Mode for full noise cancelling, or Aware Mode to bring the outside into the around ear headphones and hear your environment and your music at the same time.
• UP TO 22 HOURS BATTERY LIFE: Enjoy 22 hours of battery life from a single charge. A quick 15-minute charge offers 3 hours when you’re on the go, or plug in the included audio cable to listen for even longer in wired mode.
• PERSONALIZE YOUR AUDIO: Adjustable EQ allows you to set the bass, mid-range, and treble levels to your personal preferences or select one of several preset options.
• BOSE SIMPLESYNC TECHNOLOGY: SimpleSync pairs your Bose QuietComfort 45 headphones with select Bose smart soundbars for a personal TV listening experience. Independent volume controls allow you to lower or mute your soundbar while keeping your headphones as loud as you like.Away from your phone. Press and hold the Bluetooth button on each device to sync their sound. Already got a group going. Link by pressing the Action button to connect at a moment’s notice. Includes 3.5 mm to 2.5 mm audio cable
Review: Most high-quality earbuds out there, and compared to Sony they don't torture your ears.

Title: Sony WH-1000XM4 Wireless
Description:
Sony’s intelligent industry-leading noise canceling headphones with premium sound elevate your listening experience with the ability to personalize and control everything you hear. Get up to 30 hours of battery life with quick charging capabilities, enjoy an enhanced Smart Listening feature set, and carry conversations hands-free with speak-to-chat.

• Industry-leading noise canceling with Dual Noise Sensor technology.Specific uses for product : Communication
• Next-level music with Edge-AI, co-developed with Sony Music Studios Tokyo
• Up to 30-hour battery life with quick charging (10 min charge for 5 hours of playback)
• the WH1000XM4 Touch Sensor controls to pause play skip tracks, control volume, activate your voice assistant, and answer phone calls.
• Speak-to-chat technology automatically reduces volume during conversations
• Superior call quality with precise voice pickup. Frequency Response (Active Operation)-4Hz-40,000Hz. Frequency Response(Bluetooth Communication)- 20Hz - 20,000Hz (44.1kHz Sampling) / 20Hz - 40,000Hz (LDAC 96kHz Sampling, 990kbps)
• Wearing detection pauses playback when headphones are removed
Review: Put them on in a noisy cafe, classroom or stupid open office. Notice the world going full silent and finally concentrate. Through a lot of research I found this to be the best one.

Title: Ultimate Ears WONDERBOOM 3
Description: Shop WONDERBOOM 3. Features 360 big sound, 14HRs playtime, 40M Bluetooth range, easy pairing, made from recycled materials, IP67, and more
Review: The most durable portable speakers, ideal for travelling through their compact design. Good enough for small parties.

Title: Oura Ring 3.0
Description:
Each style has identical technical and hardware capabilities.

Water resistant up to 100 m (more than 328 ft.)
Lighter than a conventional ring (4 to 6 grams)
Titanium: durable and wearable
Includes size-specific charger and USB-C cable
With daily wear, the ring may develop scratches

Ring sensors should be on the palm side of your finger for the most accurate reading. To help ensure optimal positioning, Oura Horizon has a sleek, uninterrupted circular design with a pill-shaped dimple on the bottom, and Oura Heritage has a classic, plateau design with a flat surface on top.
Review: If you're serious about progression in fitness, a biometric tracker is key. This is the best ring version currently available.

Title: Google Nest Mini
Description: Smart Speaker for Any Room
Review: I don't use alarms anymore. I rather use this as an alarm I can just set up with my voice command, along with white noise generator for sleep. Or to have a conversation when I'm lonely.

Title: Apple 2021 MacBookPro M1 Pro chip 10-core CPU (16 inch)
Description:
Late 2021 Apple MacBookPro with Apple M1 Pro chip 10-core CPU (16 inch, 16GB RAM, 1TB SSD Storage) (QWERTY English) Silver (Renewed Premium)

• Apple M1 Pro or M1 Max chip for a massive leap in CPU, GPU, and machine learning performance
• Up to 10-core CPU delivers up to 2x faster performance to fly through pro workflows quicker than ever
• Up to 32-core GPU with up to 4x faster performance for graphics-intensive apps and games
• 16-core Neural Engine for up to 5x faster machine learning performance, Longer battery life, up to 21 hours
• Up to 64GB of unified memory so everything you do is fast and fluid
Review: Before I was a windows user. Then I realised Mac is superior.

Title: tomtoc 360 Protective Laptop Sleeve
Description: Visit the Store Visit the Store Visit the Store Visit the Store
Review: I don't understand people who don't buy protective gear for their work station. It's like a workplace helmet for Macs and should be mandatory.

Title: Ledger Nano X
Description: Make sure your crypto assets are safe anywhere you go with our most advanced hardware wallet yet. The Ledger Nano X is a bluetooth enabled secure device that offers an extensive capacity and an easy-to-use experience for crypto owners.
Review: Not your keys, not your crypto. If you leave crypto at a centralised exchange, you'll always be at risk from the whims of governmental agencies or from being blocked out of your account. Get a hardwallet, frens. Also get a hard metal plate and a metal engraver to engrave your secret key on it (of course encoded) and store them in a safe.

Title: AirTag
Description: Attach AirTag to everyday items and easily keep track of them on iPhone. Personalize with text and emoji engraving. Buy 1 or 4 pack now at apple.com.
Review: For years I thought I had the genius next billion dollar idea, until belatedly and humbingly realising that Apple had released Airtags a long time ago... In any case, this is obviously a super useful product.

Title: Sahara Sailor Water Bottles
Description: The choice for anyone looking to make a small contribution to protecting the planet. Help save the environment by not using single use product. We support the clean water project in Kono Sierra Leone. All our products carbon emissions are calculated and were offsetted.
Review: When drinking from a tumbler, make sure it's BPA-free plastic to reduce the risk of cancer. This bottle is large to reduce refill trips yet fills nicely in bottle pockets of bags.

Title: NOMATIC Backpack
Description: The Nomatic Backpack was designed for everyday use. Available in 2 sizes, 20 liters and 14 liters. It’s made with durable, water-resistant materials and YKK zippers. With 20% expansion, this bag is slim but expands when you need to pack more. The patent-pending strap system allows you to go from backpack to briefcase c
Review: I've had my Nomatic bag for over five years now. Apart from receiving compliments for how sleek it looks, people comment on how it must be new. I tell them I've used it for over five years. Seriously, this bag is so resilient and so high-quality you won't ever need a new bag. I don't know how many times I let it drop or ran through the rain with it: my laptop was always unscathed. This is probably one of the best products to emerge from Kickstarter history.

Title: Osprey Farpoint® 70 Travel Pack
Description: All your adventure-travel needs, bundled with men's-specific backpacking-carry technology, a youthfully sophisticated aesthetic and detachable daypack, perfect for a week of continuous travel.
Review: Osprey is the indisputable king of backpacks, as you will find if you conduct hours of research before asking my brother to gift it to me for my birthday. So with the brand down, for my particular needs (moving my entire livelihood in a bag) the 70L is the model to go for. I love the detachable day pack which is effectively my daily gym bag and also my short trip bag. Took to all sorts of climates, adventures in nature and around the world. Still as good as new. It's phenomenal

Title: Kindle Paperwhite (8 GB)
Description:
• Kindle Paperwhite – Now with a 6.8” display and thinner borders, adjustable warm light, up to 10 weeks of battery life, and 20% faster page turns.
• Purpose-built for reading – With a flush-front design and 300 ppi glare-free display that reads like real paper, even in bright sunlight.
• More books in more places – Store thousands of titles, then take them all with you. A single charge via USB-C last weeks, not hours.
• Easy on the eyes – Now with adjustable warm light to shift screen shade from white to amber.
• Waterproof reading – Built to withstand accidental immersion in water, so you’re good from the beach to the bath.
• Find new stories – With Kindle Unlimited, get unlimited access to over 2 million titles, thousands of audiobooks, and more.
• Go hands-free – Pair with an Audible subscription and Bluetooth headphones or speakers to listen to your story.
Review: I'm definitely the kind of guy who prefers to read from a tangible book, smell the paper and be old-school in that way. However, I just read too much and travel too much for me to haul around physical books all the time. Once I got to use the premium Kindl, I started to like it a lot. You'll get used to the non-paper aspect in no time. And your book count is guaranteed to increase. For me I tripled the amount of books I read in a year to around 30.

Title: 4Monster Camping Towels Super Absorbent
Description: Wherever you go, our products will provide you with more joy and convenience.   It all started on a camping trip to Yellowstone National Park. While four senior outdoor enthusiasts get together，the conversation took an unexpected turn to the subject of outdoor gears. Our designer friend brought an awesome travel backpack. We agreed that it was very beautiful and functional, but cost a lot. A question came to our minds: Why don't we make some practical, stylish and lightweight outdoor gear? After camping, our trip leads us to Big Sky City in Montana. Lying under the starry sky, we decided to build a functional and stylish outdoor brand.   We started with quick-drying towels and backpacks. In this year, we did various design draft and material testings. After many twist and turns, we finally resolve the basic prototypes of our original towels and backpacks. We received a lot of valuable messages from many outdoor enthusiasts which we would like to thank to.   4Monster was born, based on technical materials, and with the latest design, we are committed to creating a "portable" outdoor products brand, with minimizing size, but also aesthetic, durable, practical and fashion. 4Monster Co-funder& General Manager --------Gary & Eddy Prefect for Outdoor We really hope our customer will feel special when they carry this towel to the outdoor.So we designed a new portable case rather than a small bag. This is the third towel we designed. The first one we focus on is portable and soft. The second towel is highly absorbent and ideal for water sports. The third is a combination of the previous two models. It is soft, light and easy to carry, and also absorbs water very well. If you are not sure what you will encounter on the trip, this towel will be your first choice. 85% polyester & 15% polyamide material，the perfect combination of softness, lightness and strong water absorption. As a microfiber towel manufacturer with over 30 years history , we only bring quality product to our customer:   WASH TIPS: machion washable in cold/gentle water do not bleach do not dry clean do not iron do not tumble dry You can safely bring the 4Monster travel towel to the beach,just shake the towel, the sand will fall off Treated with SILVADUR technology.It will continue to release silver ions in the fabric . This is completely harmless to the body. We were inspired by silver tableware, which proved to be very successful. You will find a free carabiner in the package . Made of metal, it is stronger and more durable, with this you can easily hang our towel on your backpack or belt. PS：Do not use this carabiner for professional mountaineering. 4Monster microfiber camping towel can be easily put in a pocket without any extra weight. It is also an excellent space saver in a backpack or suitcase. No longer necessary to carry large and heavy towels when traveling and exercising outdoors！ Sand Free No Smell Additional Free Carabiner Portable & Light Weight 6 sizes & 12 colors,we got all your activities covered Latest EVA case rather than mesh bag,portable and keep towels clean during the trip Easily fit in a pocket or hang on a backpack 85% polyester & 15% polyamide material,perfect combination of water absorption and softness.Towels for any situation
Review: When travelling, some shitty places won't provide towels, or you don't want to impose on the friend you're staying at by using their towel. Ultra light and packable microfiber towels are the solution. This towel takes up less space than a folder t-shirt. In addition, it's absorption capacity means you can actually dry much faster than with a regular towel. Oh, it can also function as a picnic sheet. Mutlifunction-approved!

Title: Men's BauBax 3.0 Travel Jacket
Description: Functional, comfortable and stylish coverage for men and women on-the-go Description Features & Benefits The BauBax 3.0 Jacket upgrades a classic design to a new-age design with modern, utility-inspired details. A minimalistic yet functional jacket that satisfies anything you throw at it. From daily commute to memo
Review: Since I love everything efficient when it comes to travel, I need to mention Baubax, the swiss knife of jackets. It come with an inflatable neck pillow, a sleep mask, dedicated pockets for everything (phone, charger, passport, glasses, earbuds, tablets, keys, wallet), and additional features such as microfiber cleaning cloth or hand-warming pockets. Ah yes, and it's thermo-regulating. The ultimate functional jacket.

Title: Nextstand Laptop Stand
Description: Nexstand laptop stands are designed for comfort, convenience and flexibility. It's the perfect product to help you work in comfort so you don't have to suffer from aches and pains.
Review: Got my nextstand since over seven years now and mistreated it greatly. Yet it folds and unfolds and makes sure I have good posture when on my laptop as ever. Thank you nextstand.

Title: SAMSUNG 49" Odyssey Neo G9
Description: At 49 inches wide, the Samsung Odyssey Neo G Gaming Monitor fully wraps around your view, and lets you lose yourself in whatever world you decide to call home. It features an industry defining 1000R curved screen, equipped with a cutting edge Quantum Matrix HDR 2000 panel, 240hz refresh rate, G-Sync and FreeSync Premium Pro support, 1ms response rates, and fully customizable Odyssey Infinity Core lighting. Quantum Mini LED, which achieves next-generation depth, delivers exceptional picture quality, placing Odyssey Neo in its own class. It is one of Samsung’s biggest gaming monitors. With 1000R curvature inspired by the human eye, a 32:9 screen ratio, and Samsung’s unique CoreSync lighting, Odyssey Neo delivers ultimate immersion. By matching the curve of the human eye, 1000R reduces potential eye strain by up to 87%. The 49” DQHD resolution brings you a display as wide as two QHD monitors sitting side by side, with incredibly detailed, pin-sharp images. Experience a more encompassing view with maximum space to take in all the action. Game, watch, chat — all at the same time. With PBP, view input from two sources simultaneously at their native resolution.The product is multiple voltage compatible, that voltage arrange is 100-240V.
Review:
If you're the kind of person who likes productivity, you should try out an ultra-wide screen. No, you actually MUST. Having up to three screens open will supercharge knowledge work and drastically reduce the small but aggregating cognitive tasks of having to switch between different applications. This is especially relevant for programmers.
Plus, you'll just feel like a pretty cool person.

Title: LED Floor Lamp
Description: Are you tired of the usual white or warm color lighting in your home? Have you considered getting an RGB light, but are concerned that it may not provide sufficient illumination for everyday use?   Bosceos RGB LED Floor Lamp will be the ideal solution for your lighting needs!   16 Million Color & 200+ Dynamic Scene Modes - This floor lamp providing you wonderful lights that are up to 16 million color! Combined with the 200+ dynamic scene modes, you can fully enjoy the magnificence of the colored lighting and delight in the fantastic night.   Remote and App Control - This RGB floor lamp providing you 3 methods to control it: Remote control, App control and wire switch. It requires no other action, just sitting there and moving your finger, and then get everything done.   Sync with music - The color light of this corner lamp will pulsate to the beat of the music or your voice, enveloping you in a captivating and immersive musical environment. Great for watching movies, having parties, playing games, etc.    Dimmable - This LED floor lamp support stepless dimming from 0% to 100%. You can select the desired brightness level according the event and activity you are having.   Timing Function - This standing lamp allows you to schedule the lighting time via remote or app control. It can avoid unnecessary power consumption and save your cost on electricity.   Wide Application - This pole lamp can be easily put in any corner of your room, such as living room, bedroom, office, sitting room, gaming room, home theater, restaurant, bar, rest room to create perfect ambience lighting for various occasions such as party, Birthday, Christmas, family reunion, etc.
Review: According to Andrew Huberman, the eminent neuroscientist, you should avoid light from above before sleep, since it emulates the sunshine and mess around with your circadian programming. But for work, I also don't want just any reading or desk lamp, because then I go into relaxation mode. The answer: funky mutlicolored lights with scifi vibes. Can also function as mood light for le dates and all.

Title: Leuchtturm1917 Notebook
Description: • FSC-certified 80 gsm paper (B5, A5, B6+ A6 formats); 100 gsm paper (A4+ formats) • Gusseted pocket and elastic enclosure band • Numbered pages...
Review: The royalty of notebooks, German-engineered.

Title: GanKe Stahl Bitcoin Geldboerse
Description:
Die Bitcoin-Geldbörse von besteht aus 304er Edelstahl mit einem Schmelzpunkt von über 1371°C (2500°F). Sie wurde als konservierend, feuerfest, wasserdicht, stoßfest und hackerfest entwickelt und getestet
Unsere Krypto-Brieftasche ist außen unmarkiert und ohne Markenzeichen und mit manipulationssicheren Aufklebern. Die einzigartigen holographischen Aufkleber dienen dazu, die Kryptowährungs-Brieftasche zu versiegeln und Manipulationsnachweise zu erbringen. Gebrochene oder ersetzte Aufkleber zeigen an, ob Ihr Bitcoin Steel Walllet geöffnet wurde.
Enthält ein Passphrasenfeld - arbeitet zusammen mit der BIP39-Wortliste, ist jedoch mit jedem 12- oder 24-Wort-Seed in jeder Sprache kompatibel und eignet sich perfekt zum Speichern Ihrer privaten Kryptowährungsinformationen oder für jeden Fall, in dem ein privates Kühlsystem erforderlich ist
Es ist mit allen BIP39-Wallets kompatibel, funktioniert mit allen Hardware-Wallets, einschließlich TREZOR, Ledger Nano S und KeepKey, und unterstützt bis zu 24 Mnemonics-Startphrasen
You can lock it up if you still feel unsafe,the bottom hole on bitcoin wallet is 6mm/0.24inch. ( Please note that The screws we provided are not for 6MM holes, The bottom 6MM hole can be locked with a lock. )
Review: Not your keys, not your crypto. If you leave crypto at a centralised exchange, you'll always be at risk from the whims of governmental agencies or from being blocked out of your account. Get a hardwallet, frens. Also get a hard metal plate and a metal engraver to engrave your secret key on it (of course encoded) and store them in a safe.

Title: Dremel 2050 Stylo+ Multifunktionswerkzeug
Description:
Das Multifunktionswerkzeug-System Dremel 2050 Stylo+ für eine Vielzahl von kreativen Anwendungen
Komfortables Arbeiten und maximale Kontrolle dank leichtem und kompaktem Design des Werkzeugs
Einfacher und schneller Wechsel von Zubehören durch das enthaltene Bohrfutter 4486
Die variable Drehzahleinstellung von 5.000 bis 22.000 U/min ermöglicht kreative Aufgaben mit zahlreichen Materialen wie Glas, Holz, Leder, Stein und Metall
GARANTIE: Standardmäßig 2 Jahre Garantie. Erhalte 1 Jahr extra, wenn du dein Dremel Werkzeug auf My Dremel registrierst
Review: Not your keys, not your crypto. If you leave crypto at a centralised exchange, you'll always be at risk from the whims of governmental agencies or from being blocked out of your account. Get a hardwallet, frens. Also get a hard metal plate and a metal engraver to engrave your secret key on it (of course encoded) and store them in a safe.

Title: Bodhi Yogamatte ECO PRO DIAMOND
Description:
Yoga, Meditation, ganzheitliche Fitness - Produkte für deine Praxis & einen entspannten Lifestyle. Join the #bodhifamily! bodhi ist eine Marke der bodhifamily von Bodynova. Die Ideen & Designs entstehen in Köln in einem Team von unterschiedlichsten Menschen, die eine Vision teilen. Wir begleiten Yogis seit über 20 Jahren mit Yoga & Pilates Zubehör, Yogakleidung, Meditationsbedarf und Lifestyle-Accessoires. Du willst mehr über die Menschen und Produkte rund um bodhi erfahren? Besuche unsere bodhi Markenwelt und verbinde dich mit uns und der #bodhifamily! Vom 2-Mann-Betrieb im Jahr 1998 wuchsen wir aus eigener Kraft zu einem heute 40-köpfigen internationalen Versandhandel für Yoga & Meditation, Pilates Equipment und Massagebedarf heran. Wir legen viel Wert auf bezahlbare Preise, liebevollen Kreationen und praxistaugliche Produkte. Ebenso wichtig für uns: Fairness & Transparenz für alle Beteiligten, ohne Preisdumping und Ausbeutung. Weil wir aus eigener Erfahrung wissen, dass Yoga, Meditation & Self Care die Schlüssel für ein erfüllteres, friedlicheres und gesünderes Leben für alle sind. Shop besuchen

• NATÜRLICH & RUTSCHFEST: Unsere rutschfeste Yogamatte aus Naturkautschuk verbindet die besten Eigenschaften einer Matte mit den hoechsten oekologischen Standards. Die Matte ist sehr hochwertig verarbeitet, wodurch eine extrem hohe Rutschfestigkeit mit einer sehr guten Daempfung entsteht
• 100 % ÖKOLOGISCH: Die Yogamatte besteht aus 100% biologisch abbaubarem Naturkautschuk und ist frei von jeglichen Chemikalien, Allergenen und Schadstoffen. Zertifiziert ist die Matte ist mit dem hoechsten Öko-Tex Standard 100, Klasse I, welcher die Unbedenklichkeit bei Hautkontakt sogar bei Babyartikeln garantiert: (Pruefnummer 2012OK0503)
• ULTRA GRIP: Die EcoPro Mat eignet sich fuer alle Yogis, die eine besonders griffigen Yogamatte suchen und ein Abrutschen sowie ein Verrutschen der Matte vermeiden moechten. Die hohe Haptik ermoeglicht auch bei fortgeschrittenen Übungen die korrekte Ausrichtung und eine sichere Ausfuehrung. Wichtig: Je griffiger und stumpfer die Oberflaeche einer Yogamatte ist, desto groesser ist zwangslaeufig auch ihr Abrieb! Die Funktionalitaet und Rutschfestigkeit wird hierdurch aber nicht beeintraechtigt!
• VIELSEITIG: Unsere Matte ist immer und ueberall die perfekte Grundlage fuer deine Yogapraxis – egal ob Zuhause oder im Studio. Die Matte ist durch ihre hohe Haftung und Daempfung auch ideal fuer eine intensivere Yogapraxis wie Hot Yoga geeignet. Abmessungen: 185 x 60 cm | Dicke: 6 mm | Gewicht: 2,1 kg
• PFLEGELEICHT: Die Rutschfestigkeit bietet auch waehrend schweisstreibenden Einheiten einen hervorragenden Grip. Anschliessend ist die Matte sehr pflegeleicht und kann ganz einfach mit einem feuchten Tuch abgewischt oder unter der Dusche abgebraust werden
Review:
What kind of poses you can accomplish or hold for longer periods depends greatly on grip – especially for people with waterfall sweaty palms. After quite some research this one emerged for me and does the job.

Fun fact: the material that makes yoga mats sticky is also used in US-toast. That is, edible toast. The substance is banned in the EU. Like, wtf?

Title: Four Sigmatic Organic Mushroom Coffee with Lion's Mane & Chaga
Description:
Our Finnish grandparents brewed mushrooms when they couldn’t get coffee. Turns out those mushrooms—Chaga—are a powerful, immune-supporting Four Sigmatic food. That gave us an idea.

We searched for more exhaustively-studied, practically-magic ingredients to add to our daily go-tos. Guess what? Organic coffee plus Chaga is chaga-bly delicious and remarkably good at balancing caffeine.
Review: Regular coffee get's me jiterry. That's why tea is superior, since it's accompanied by the calming effects of L-theanine. OR MUSHROOMS! Chaga and Lion's mane provide phenomenal focus without the side effects of too much coffee. Plus they're just allround good for your health.

Title: Logitech MX Anywhere 3
Description: Buy MX Anywhere 3 Business Mouse. Features MagSpeed™ scroll wheel, secure wireless, 6 customizable buttons, easy switch, logi bolt receiver, and more
Review: Rather expensive small mouse, but it's so powerful. No jitteryness, super long-lasting, long battery-life, feels good in the hand – and durable! I don't know how squashed and pounded it's already been as I carry it out with me literally every day. And it's still doing it's job as always. Love this little fellow.

Title: Anker Nano II
Description:
Wir wünschen, dass du deinen Alltag ohne Unannehmlichkeiten und Unsicherheiten durchlebst und unterwegs und zuhause immer mit mehr als genug Power ausgestattet bist. Unser Ladezubehör versorgt deine Geräte nicht nur mit Energie, sondern bietet dir auch zusätzliche technische Funktionen und absolute Sicherheit. Shop besuchen Shop besuchen Shop besuchen Shop besuchen Shop besuchen

• DER EINE FÜR ALLES: Ankers weltberuehmte Ladetechnologie garantiert blitzschnelle Ladungen fuer so gut wie jedes Geraet - ob Smartphones, Tablets oder Notebooks. Und das in einem winzigen, federleichten USB-C Ladegeraet.
• HIGH-SPEED LADELEISTUNG: Lade ein 2020 MacBook Air mit Hoechstgeschwindigkeit, ein iPhone 12 mit dreifacher Geschwindigkeit sowie die neuesten Samsung Geraete mit Samsung Super Fast Charging Ladeoption.
• KOMPAKTES DESIGN: Das ultimative Design von Anker: Fantastische Effizienz bei weniger Waermeerzeugung in einem federleichten, um 34% kleineren Format im Vergleich zu Standard-Ladegeraeten.
• POWERED BY GaN II TECHNOLOGIE: Mit einer 20%-igen Verbesserung der Betriebsfrequenz, einem innovativen minimalistischen Design und einer verbesserten Leiterstruktur ermoeglicht die GaN II-Technologie ein neues, winziges, kompaktes Ladegeraet, ohne auch nur ein Element an Leistung zu verlieren.
• WAS DU BEKOMMST: Ein Anker Nano II 45W Ladegeraet, eine Bedienungsanleitung. (Ladekabel nicht im Lieferumfang enthalten.)
Review: Super useful and travel-friendly USBC charger. Can charger your phone, laptop very fast. Not as fast as the fast chargers native to your devise, but definitely speedy. And you don't have to carry the Mac charger brick around with you. I leave that at home, and take the Anker with me everytime I'm out.

Title: Zungenreiniger Edelstahl 100%
Description:
Unsere Geschichte beginnt mit einer tiefgründigen Leidenschaft, Individuen zu helfen, ein Leben der Gesundheit und des Wohlbefindens zu führen. Wir sind bei jedem Schritt und Tritt für Sie da. Wir verstehen, dass die Bedürfnisse jeder Person einzigartig sind, daher bieten wir eine umfassende Palette hochwertiger Gesundheitsprodukten an, die auf ihre spezifischen Bedürfnisse zugeschnitten sind.

• ✅ BESTES ANTIMIKROBIELLES MATERIAL: Verschiedene Studien haben bewiesen, dass glattes Edelstahl langfristig besser gegen Keime wirkt als Kupfer.
• ✅ PREMIUM PRODUKT DESIGN: Extra stabile und keimfreie Griffe aus 100% Edelstahl + eine Baumwolltasche fuer den Transport!
• ✅ FRISCHER ATEM: Die Reduzierung von Bakterien auf der Zunge bekaempft die Ursachen fuer schlechten Atem und verbessert die Mundhygiene.
• ✅ VERBESSERTER GESCHMACK: Die Zungenbuerste entfernt die weisse Schicht auf der Zunge, hierdurch verbessert sich ihr Geschmackserlebnis.
• ✅ PASST IMMER: Durch das flexible Material ist unser Produkt fuer jede Mundgroesse geeignet. Biegen Sie es einfach einfach auf Ihre Groesse.
Review: Along with my daily teethbrushing and flossing, I scrape my tongue like a good dentist's patient. However, I found over the years that the plastic ones or bristle ones are far inferior to stainless steel ones. This is a good, cheap option.

Title: Swirl Brillen-Putztuecher
Description:
• Geeignet auch fuer Glaeser und Brillen, die nicht glaenzend sind, Kunststoff-Glaeser.
• Bereits abschliessende Reinigung aller Arten von Glas durch extraweiches Tuch
• Einzeln verpackt, fuer Zuhause oder auf Reisen.
• Streifenfreier Glanz in Sekunden
• Griff in der Spenderbox 30
Review: If you're a glasses-nerd like me, get wet wipes for glasses. Believe me, it's totally different to just wiping your classes with your t-shirt or even microfiber towels. It'll change the way you see the world.

Title: Logitech MX Keys Advanced Wireless Illuminated Keyboard
Description: Introducing MX Keys, an advanced wireless illuminated keyboard crafted for efficiency, stability, and precision. Perfect Stroke keys are shaped for your fingertips and increased key stability reduces noise while optimizing responsiveness. Tactile reference for hand positioning makes it easy to stay oriented and in your flow. The backlit keys light up the moment your hands approach, and automatically adjust to suit changing lighting conditions. MX Keys follows your MX Master 3 - or other Flow-enabled mouse - from one computer to another, meaning you can type on multiple devices in one fluid workflow (2). With MX Keys you can truly master what you make.
Review: Along with my MX mouse, this beast of a keyboard is essential for me to work well. Your fingers just flow over it. Plus, like the mouse, it's been squashed and pounded around in my backpack for ages, and still stoically works as if new. Never had issues of them not working because of dust or sand or all that bullshit. They're just durable and they just work. Worth spending a couple more dollars imo.
